minlab (1.0.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release
  * Interactive game mode with level editor
  * Terminal UI with tabbed interface (Solution, Instructions, Stats, History)
  * Comprehensive keyboard shortcuts:
    - Tab: Switch between tabs
    - F5: Compile and test solution
    - F6: Toggle help screen
    - F12: Reset solution to template (with confirmation)
    - Alt+Up/Down: Move lines
    - Alt+Backspace/Shift+Delete: Delete words
    - Ctrl+Left/Right: Word navigation
  * Real-time syntax checking with line number reporting
  * Circuit simulation with truth table validation
  * Progress tracking and solution history
  * Auto-save functionality
  * Template generation for each level

